  "blurb": "A five-bedroom villa set on a hilltop above Naithon Beach, its 17-metre infinity pool opening to a wide ocean view on Phuket's quieter northwest coast. Game room, fitness and spa, and both indoor and outdoor dining sit across some 1,225 m², with a four-strong team and a private chef, sleeping up to ten.",
  "detail": "High on a hilltop above Naithon Beach, on Phuket's quieter northwest coast, this five-bedroom villa is arranged to make the most of a long ocean horizon. A 17-metre infinity pool runs toward the view, with an outdoor BBQ and dining terrace positioned for sunsets over the water.\n\nThe house is laid out as nine linked sections across roughly 1,225 m² — a master and four guest bedrooms, open living spaces, a fully equipped kitchen, a home office, and a combined spa and fitness room. A TV and game room, complete with a mahjong table, gives the group somewhere to gather after dark.\n\nIndoor and outdoor dining, Apple TV and Netflix, flatscreen televisions with a premium cable package and high-speed WiFi throughout keep the villa comfortable for a longer stay, while safety boxes, a baby cot and high chair and a two-car garage cover the practical side.\n\nA team of four, including a private chef, runs the day-to-day, with housekeeping, turndown and a complimentary return airport transfer included; car and van hire, in-house massage, laundry and a wine selection are arranged on request. The estate is gated with 24-hour security, minutes from Naithon's beach and the island's northern beaches.",
